[SCENIC_ROUTING.md](mdc:SCENIC_ROUTING.md)

Prioritize:
- 2 lane roads
- "secondary" roads
- roads with speed limit 45-65mph
- contiguous routing

De-prioritize:
- roads that are not twisty


Exclude altogether:
- unpaved roads
- roads less than 2 lanes
- any waypoint that causes retracing our steps (out-and-back). loops are allowed but not retracing steps.

Filtering mechanism:
- use OSM meta data about the street characteristics to drive our logic
- do NOT use the names of streets as part of the logic
